---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="relative w-full z-50 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 bg-clrWhite">
	<div class="w-full px-5 mt-24 md:mt-52 lg:mt-32">
		<section class="relative flex flex-col items-start justify-end md:justify-center w-full h-64 md:h-auto gap-2.5 rounded-2xl px-8 py-9 bg-secondaryNeutral">
			<section class="absolute bottom-32 md:bottom-1 lg:bottom-4 right-2 lg:right-8 w-full">
				<img class="relative z-50 float-right w-2/5 max-w-60" src="/src/assets/chibi_moe.svg" alt="Logo">
				<div class="absolute z-40 flex flex-col p-6 mr-24 md:mr-52 md:right-0 md:left-60 lg:left-auto md:top-40 md:w-2/4 lg:text-lg text-clrWhite rounded-2xl bg-primaryNeutral">
					<p>Vous souhaitez me faire passer un message ou voir mes travaux sur mes réseaux sociaux ?</p>
					<p>N’hésitez-pas !</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="flex flex-col justify-end h-full gap-2 lg:gap-14">
				<p class="text-clrWhite lg:text-3xl">On se contacte ?</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
					<a class="text-base text-clrWhite" href="mailto:carolane.noel@outlook.com">carolane.noel@outlook.com</a>
					<ul class="flex gap-8">
						<li><img src="/src/assets/logo_behance.svg" alt="Logo Behance"></li>
						<li><img src="/src/assets/logo_linkedin.svg" alt="Logo LinkedIn"></li>
						<li><img src="/src/assets/logo_instagram.svg" alt="Logo Instagram"></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			
		</section>
	</div>
	
	<section class="relative w-full">
		<img src="/src/assets/footer-illu.png" alt="Illustration footer">
		<div class="absolute w-full bottom-2 text-base text-center text-clrWhite">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Carolane. Tous droits réservés.
		</div>
	</section>
	
</footer>
